51-| `SessionReplayer`      | new (`src/session-replayer.ts`) | Loads a bundle (or sink); opens a paused `World` at any tick; runs replay self-check.                |
52:| `SessionBundle`        | new (in `src/session-bundle.ts`) | Versioned JSON-compatible archive type; shared by `SessionRecorder.toBundle()` and `ScenarioRunner.toBundle()`. |
