474-- `package.json` — version bumps per the per-commit policy in `AGENTS.md` (current version v0.7.6). All additions in this spec are additive and non-breaking, so each shipped commit gets a `c`-bump (e.g., v0.7.7 for the recorder commit, v0.7.8 for the replayer commit, and so on). No `b`-bump expected for this spec.
